```plantuml
@startuml eProsima_FIWARE-SH
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "Integration Service" as IS

rectangle "System Handle (SH)" as SH {
  rectangle "NGSIV2Connector" as Connector #lightsteelblue
  rectangle "Listener" as Listener #lightyellow
  rectangle "Publisher" as Publisher #aliceblue
  rectangle "Subscriber" as Subscriber #mistyrose
}

rectangle "FIWARE Context Broker" as FIWARE #palegreen

' ========== Connections ==========
IS --> SH : Initialize System Handle

' System Handle interactions
SH --> Connector : Configure connection to FIWARE\nvia YAML file
SH --> Listener : Start listening for notifications\nusing asio

' Connector interactions
Connector --> FIWARE : Create entity / Update attributes\nRegister/Unregister subscriptions\nvia NGSIv2 API
FIWARE --> Connector : Send notifications

' Listener interactions
Listener --> Connector : Forward received notifications

' Publisher and Subscriber interactions
Publisher --> Connector : Publish data to FIWARE\nvia NGSIv2
Subscriber --> Connector : Subscribe and receive data\nfrom FIWARE

@enduml
```